13
00:02:47,039 --> 00:02:48,080
How'd you reach

14
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:48,960
The Poet?

15
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,520
I tried before,

16
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:52,000
