36
00:03:41,879 --> 00:03:42,520
[I know.]

37
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:44,479
[Just say what I told you.]

38
00:03:48,039 --> 00:03:49,080
If you really

39
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:50,319
