41
00:03:52,039 --> 00:03:52,960
What are you, a kid?

42
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,360
Now the evidence
is right here,

43
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,680
of course we'll help the client

44
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:02,639
