45
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:05,280
[Those two guys…]

46
00:04:08,039 --> 00:04:09,199
Yeah…

47
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,039
Right.

48
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,680
Mr. Liu,

49
