53
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,079
and your skills.

54
00:04:25,079 --> 00:04:25,560
From your
performance on

55
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,319
this case,

56
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,160
I suggest

57
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:31,639
I take the lead.

58
00:04:33,959 --> 00:04:36,040
[They're already at each other's throats?]

59
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,000
Well.

60
00:04:41,519 --> 00:04:42,439
Very well!

61
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,519
Sure!

62
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:55,160
[Mr. Liu, don't take it to heart.]

63
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:57,040
