104
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:56,839
It's late.

105
00:06:57,519 --> 00:06:58,279
Sorry
for keeping you.

106
00:07:00,079 --> 00:07:00,839
How about I treat you…

107
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:04,920
and Mr. Xu

108
00:07:05,199 --> 00:07:06,120
