114
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:23,199
Really, never again!

115
00:07:23,639 --> 00:07:26,160
Director, don't give it back.

116
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,800
She'll play again.

117
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:28,920
She really will!

118
00:07:30,079 --> 00:07:30,800
What are you two doing?

119
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:32,399
Doing a comedy skit?

120
00:07:32,879 --> 00:07:33,879
Call home already!

121
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:34,759
Director,

122
00:07:34,759 --> 00:07:36,360
