Think I can't even handle you two?

130
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:56,319
Big shot, huh?

131
00:08:06,639 --> 00:08:07,360
Abroad, right?

132
00:08:13,399 --> 00:08:13,920
Hello,

133
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:15,959
I'm Feng Zhu,

134
00:08:16,279 --> 00:08:17,360
Huaishi Xu's teacher.

135
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,360
Today…

136
00:08:18,839 --> 00:08:19,240
This…

137
00:08:19,839 --> 00:08:20,839
