138
00:08:21,279 --> 00:08:22,040
Great.

139
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:22,920
Here's the thing.

140
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:24,639
I'm Zhu Feng, head of moral ed

141
00:08:24,839 --> 00:08:25,279
