145
00:08:30,639 --> 00:08:31,759
First time

146
00:08:31,759 --> 00:08:32,720
I noticed,

147
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:34,320
but the issue's…

148
00:08:34,759 --> 00:08:35,519
[Sorry,]

149
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:36,600
I can't handle it
at the moment.

150
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,039
Please contact
her guardian.

151
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:41,639
Number 133…

152
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:42,759
Hold on.

153
00:08:44,879 --> 00:08:45,440
Bro,

154
00:08:45,799 --> 00:08:47,440
[that's betrayal]

155
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,279
[and revenge!]

156
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,440
You're getting back at me

157
00:08:50,639 --> 00:08:51,679
for peeking at your texts.

158
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:53,440
By the way,

159
00:08:53,799 --> 00:08:54,720
this isn't the first time

160
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:55,919
she brought her phone.

161
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,080
Once you

162
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:58,440
reach her guardian,

163
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,320
please explain

164
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:02,000
