173
00:09:20,679 --> 00:09:21,440
What?

174
00:09:22,559 --> 00:09:23,240
Why laughing?

175
00:09:24,919 --> 00:09:25,679
1,500 words for you!

176
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:31,360
You and your sister

177
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,440
