178
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,600
She's in trouble,

179
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,759
and you didn't even cover for her.

180
00:09:36,399 --> 00:09:37,600
She has caused

181
00:09:40,039 --> 00:09:41,080
