182
00:09:41,799 --> 00:09:42,600
Can't fix it all.

183
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,600
Thanks so much,

184
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:51,960
Lawyers Xu and Liu

185
00:09:52,039 --> 00:09:52,840
