190
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:02,759
Then have something else.

191
00:10:03,799 --> 00:10:04,600
A cola for you?

192
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:07,480
Unhealthy.

193
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:11,879
Hello,

194
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,240
