199
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:23,840
Yeah.

200
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,720
Here, try this.

201
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,240
Know them?

202
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:06,000
Miss Ruan, a reminder.

203
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,279
Taking photos

204
00:11:07,279 --> 00:11:08,759
