206
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:14,039
I'm not just snapping photos,

207
00:11:14,039 --> 00:11:15,080
I'm throwing punches too.

208
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:16,600
Need help?
No, private matter.

209
00:11:18,919 --> 00:11:20,039
That perfume

210
00:11:20,559 --> 00:11:21,480
