your girlfriend.

216
00:11:29,919 --> 00:11:31,000
Why don't I think

217
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:31,320
it fits

218
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:32,480
her vibe?

219
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,919
Yu, fancy meeting you here.

220
00:11:36,399 --> 00:11:38,480
Yeah, what a coincidence.

221
00:11:38,919 --> 00:11:39,960
If not,

222
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,519
I wouldn't see this.

223
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:45,279
Who do you think that guy is?

224
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:47,720
Didn't you hear her?

225
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:48,759
Private matter.

226
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:51,639
Definitely an ex.

227
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,559
Just an ex,

228
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,039
