229
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:59,840
No love, no hate.

230
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,840
Still not over it.

231
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:09,840
Let me introduce.

232
00:12:10,519 --> 00:12:11,240
This is Ms. Lin,

233
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,600
