234
00:12:14,039 --> 00:12:14,799
And this is my…

235
00:12:14,799 --> 00:12:16,519
I'm Zhang Chuan's girlfriend's bestie.

236
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:20,399
Ms. Lin, you probably didn't know

237
00:12:20,679 --> 00:12:21,679
