238
00:12:22,919 --> 00:12:23,679
Well,

239
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:25,200
business is business,
not romance.

240
00:12:26,559 --> 00:12:27,840
No need to share personal stuff.

241
00:12:28,639 --> 00:12:29,600
Right, Chuan?

242
00:12:30,799 --> 00:12:31,360
Right.

243
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:39,200
Many want to do business with me,

244
00:12:39,759 --> 00:12:40,799
