245
00:12:41,519 --> 00:12:43,039
Why should I deal with you?

246
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:46,320
Ms. Lin…

247
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,559
Yu, you misunderstood me.

248
00:12:54,559 --> 00:12:55,360
Misunderstood what?
I really…

249
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:58,000
What's going on?

250
00:13:02,039 --> 00:13:02,679
Who's this?

251
00:13:03,559 --> 00:13:04,559
My girlfriend's bestie.

252
00:13:07,759 --> 00:13:09,360
A bit nosy, huh?

253
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:11,639
We were cooperating fine,

254
00:13:11,639 --> 00:13:12,919
