258
00:13:18,159 --> 00:13:19,320
Holding hands, what's wrong?

259
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:21,120
I just touched your hand,
- so what?
- What are you doing?

260
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:22,919
- I just did it!
- What?

261
00:13:23,159 --> 00:13:23,799
- You…
- I just…

262
00:14:00,159 --> 00:14:02,159
And who are you?

263
00:14:03,799 --> 00:14:05,039
I'm her lawyer.

264
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:07,000
Sir,

265
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,240
I must remind you.

266
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:09,879
Under Civil Code,

267
00:14:09,879 --> 00:14:10,960
Art. 1010,

268
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,399
if someone sexually harasses another

269
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:13,840
against their will

270
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:15,639
via touch,

271
00:14:16,279 --> 00:14:17,679
the victim can

272
00:14:17,679 --> 00:14:20,080
seek civil damages.

273
00:14:22,799 --> 00:14:24,039
Bringing a lawyer to dinner?

274
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:25,720
