277
00:14:38,399 --> 00:14:38,960
You okay?

278
00:14:42,039 --> 00:14:42,480
Come along.

279
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:46,679
Sorry,

280
00:14:47,039 --> 00:14:48,440
got held up by some

281
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:49,720
