283
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:53,799
No worries, we were all eating fine.

284
00:14:53,799 --> 00:14:54,600
Right, Huaisong?

285
00:14:56,080 --> 00:14:57,320
Yeah, but you seem late.

286
00:15:01,039 --> 00:15:02,279
Next client meeting.

287
00:15:08,519 --> 00:15:09,200
Right, right.

288
00:15:09,799 --> 00:15:10,200
Well,
thanks for the heads-up.

289
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,120
I'd have forgotten otherwise.

290
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:13,200
Yu, I've got something to do,

291
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:14,080
