292
00:15:16,320 --> 00:15:16,960
Let him take you.

293
00:15:19,759 --> 00:15:20,440
No need,
I'll just grab a taxi.

294
00:15:21,559 --> 00:15:22,080
No!

295
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:23,879
Don't take a taxi, not safe.

296
00:15:23,879 --> 00:15:24,639
What if you

297
00:15:24,639 --> 00:15:25,960
run into those two again? You…

298
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:31,480
Get in.

299
00:15:35,399 --> 00:15:35,799
Go ahead.

300
00:15:37,399 --> 00:15:38,320
