547
00:31:40,720 --> 00:31:42,240
What are you drinking, Mr. Xu?

548
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:44,559
Black coffee?

549
00:31:45,319 --> 00:31:46,240
I've never seen anyone

550
00:31:46,240 --> 00:31:47,640
drink it in such

551
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:48,480
