565
00:32:50,119 --> 00:32:51,039
[Yeah, go ahead.]

566
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:53,359
Here's the thing.

567
00:32:53,960 --> 00:32:55,160
I was gonna have my lawyer

568
00:32:55,519 --> 00:32:57,039
