585
00:33:34,359 --> 00:33:35,759
Sure, see you there.

586
00:33:39,759 --> 00:33:41,079
She might be on guard.

587
00:33:41,880 --> 00:33:43,119
It takes about

588
00:33:43,119 --> 00:33:43,759
