don't want any slip-ups.

590
00:33:47,319 --> 00:33:48,119
You going solo?

591
00:33:50,799 --> 00:33:51,799
Should be fine.

592
00:33:55,960 --> 00:33:56,920
You only get one shot.

593
00:33:58,480 --> 00:33:59,079
I'll go with you.

594
00:34:09,440 --> 00:34:10,000
Recorder.

595
00:34:10,840 --> 00:34:11,679
Push up to record,

596
00:34:12,039 --> 00:34:12,760
down to save.

597
00:34:33,079 --> 00:34:33,960
Thanks, Mr. Xu.

598
00:35:05,719 --> 00:35:07,239
I thought coaxing info over the phone

599
00:35:07,719 --> 00:35:08,599
would be easy.

600
00:35:09,480 --> 00:35:10,599
But now,

601
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:13,559
my heart's racing.

602
00:35:20,159 --> 00:35:21,320
Let's do some eye exercises.

603
00:35:26,400 --> 00:35:27,760
Looks like it works

604
00:35:28,440 --> 00:35:29,199
in your novel.

605
00:35:59,599 --> 00:36:01,280
[Sorry, I grabbed the wrong one.]

606
00:36:02,440 --> 00:36:03,920
The wrong one.

607
00:36:05,559 --> 00:36:06,079
Then,

608
00:36:07,079 --> 00:36:08,639
who's the right one?

609
00:36:14,519 --> 00:36:15,159
Jerk!

610
00:36:21,000 --> 00:36:21,840
Novels are

611
00:36:22,960 --> 00:36:23,800
all smoke and mirrors.

612
00:36:28,320 --> 00:36:29,960
[Eye exercises are bogus…]

613
00:36:31,360 --> 00:36:33,840
[and so is 'liking me?']

614
00:36:38,519 --> 00:36:40,199
[Eye exercises don't work at all.]

615
00:36:41,519 --> 00:36:42,800
[That day, yelling 'jerk']

616
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:43,800
[a hundred times]

617
00:36:44,480 --> 00:36:46,400
[finally calmed me down.]

618
00:37:07,599 --> 00:37:08,159
Yu,

619
00:37:09,239 --> 00:37:10,679
thanks for giving me this chance

620
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:12,159
to explain in person.

621
00:37:14,880 --> 00:37:17,039
I've thought it through, Sisi.

622
00:37:18,239 --> 00:37:19,360
Settlement's fine.

623
00:37:21,599 --> 00:37:22,960
But my lawyer isn't just

624
00:37:23,280 --> 00:37:24,559
looking out for me,

625
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:26,039
they're thinking about the adaptation.

626
00:37:27,159 --> 00:37:28,159
To protect

627
00:37:28,239 --> 00:37:29,679
the adaptation,

628
00:37:30,599 --> 00:37:31,320
they want you

629
00:37:31,320 --> 00:37:32,599
to admit in your apology

630
00:37:33,639 --> 00:37:35,119
that you not only posted

631
00:37:35,119 --> 00:37:36,119
slanderous long posts about me

632
00:37:36,599 --> 00:37:38,079
but also stirred online attacks.

633
00:37:39,239 --> 00:37:39,639
I…

634
00:37:40,639 --> 00:37:41,800
I didn't.

635
00:37:45,320 --> 00:37:46,840
I know this statement

636
00:37:46,840 --> 00:37:47,960
is rough,

637
00:37:49,440 --> 00:37:50,679
but the production company

638
00:37:50,679 --> 00:37:51,599
says if we

639
00:37:51,599 --> 00:37:53,239
can't settle, they'll sue.

640
00:37:54,400 --> 00:37:56,400
But Yu, I…

641
00:37:58,079 --> 00:38:00,320
I didn't aim to attack you.

642
00:38:01,480 --> 00:38:02,440
When I posted that,
I honestly

643
00:38:03,800 --> 00:38:04,840
thought that's

644
00:38:04,840 --> 00:38:05,679
how it was.

645
00:38:06,920 --> 00:38:07,800
I had no idea

646
00:38:07,800 --> 00:38:08,880
you are Lily Vale.

647
00:38:09,519 --> 00:38:10,440
That post
then went viral

648
00:38:11,280 --> 00:38:12,199
on its own,

649
00:38:12,559 --> 00:38:13,800
had nothing to do with me.

650
00:38:14,199 --> 00:38:15,840
Just the internet running wild.

651
00:38:19,079 --> 00:38:19,639
Sisi,

652
00:38:20,760 --> 00:38:21,920
the web isn't lawless.

653
00:38:22,559 --> 00:38:23,360
Everything leaves

654
00:38:23,360 --> 00:38:24,519
a trail.

655
00:38:25,199 --> 00:38:26,440
Even if you deny it now,

656
00:38:26,880 --> 00:38:27,920
it'll show up

657
00:38:28,079 --> 00:38:28,960
in the investigation later.

658
00:38:31,639 --> 00:38:32,360
We went to

659
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:33,719
the same school.

660
00:38:34,679 --> 00:38:35,639
You're my junior.

661
00:38:37,320 --> 00:38:38,639
Of course I don't want things

662
00:38:39,559 --> 00:38:40,519
to get messy.

663
00:38:42,599 --> 00:38:43,079
So…

664
00:38:45,159 --> 00:38:46,199
Yu,

665
00:38:47,559 --> 00:38:49,079
could you drop the case for now?

666
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:52,079
You can still

667
00:38:52,199 --> 00:38:53,280
have your lawyer

668
00:38:53,280 --> 00:38:54,480
check things out later.

669
00:38:55,079 --> 00:38:56,199
Let's settle this quietly,

670
00:38:56,199 --> 00:38:57,079
no drama.

671
00:38:57,480 --> 00:38:58,519
Isn't that better?

672
00:39:02,079 --> 00:39:03,320
That could work.

673
00:39:05,199 --> 00:39:06,320
But if I drop it,

674
00:39:07,039 --> 00:39:08,360
someone sneaky

675
00:39:08,760 --> 00:39:10,360
might twist it against me

676
00:39:11,159 --> 00:39:12,039
and stir up The Poet
to sue.

677
00:39:13,599 --> 00:39:14,480
What then?

678
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:18,880
You're overthinking it, isn't it?

679
00:39:32,239 --> 00:39:33,559
[If things stall,]

680
00:39:33,800 --> 00:39:35,400
[try to switch gears]

681
00:39:35,880 --> 00:39:36,920
[and change the topic.]

682
00:39:36,920 --> 00:39:38,079
[Play along with her,]

683
00:39:38,280 --> 00:39:39,440
[let her guard down.]

684
00:39:51,159 --> 00:39:51,719
Sisi.

685
00:39:56,719 --> 00:39:57,400
Actually,

686
00:39:59,239 --> 00:40:00,519
I've been having a really rough time.

687
00:40:04,079 --> 00:40:04,679
I know,

688
00:40:06,119 --> 00:40:07,400
at this rate,

689
00:40:09,719 --> 00:40:10,639
the adaptation rights
won't sell.

690
00:40:12,199 --> 00:40:13,039
If this keeps up,

691
00:40:14,039 --> 00:40:14,880
the site could

692
00:40:14,880 --> 00:40:16,159
drop me any minute.

693
00:40:19,280 --> 00:40:20,639
That won't happen.

694
00:40:22,039 --> 00:40:23,599
You're the cash cow.

695
00:40:25,480 --> 00:40:26,800
Authors come and go,

696
00:40:26,800 --> 00:40:27,559
fast.

697
00:40:28,280 --> 00:40:29,719
Once Qianhe kicks me out,

698
00:40:31,039 --> 00:40:32,119
no other site will

699
00:40:32,119 --> 00:40:33,000
touch me either.

700
00:40:37,599 --> 00:40:39,400
Yu, you worry too much.

701
00:40:39,800 --> 00:40:41,199
Even if the worst happens,

702
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:42,079
Shican

703
00:40:42,079 --> 00:40:43,599
wouldn't just sit back.

704
00:40:44,760 --> 00:40:46,280
After all, he owes you

705
00:40:46,280 --> 00:40:47,199
from back in school.

706
00:40:47,960 --> 00:40:48,480
Right?

707
00:40:49,480 --> 00:40:50,559
He's so busy right now,

708
00:40:51,599 --> 00:40:53,119
he won't bother with stuff like this.

709
00:40:56,760 --> 00:40:57,719
I was thinking,

710
00:41:00,320 --> 00:41:02,079
if you really hired the army of fans,

711
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:04,519
at least with Shican in the loop,

712
00:41:05,599 --> 00:41:07,000
I could still appeal to you.

713
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:15,519
Or…

714
00:41:18,639 --> 00:41:19,880
you could just beg me, right?

715
00:41:26,039 --> 00:41:26,960
So it was you.

716
00:41:30,599 --> 00:41:31,679
You knew from the start

717
00:41:31,679 --> 00:41:32,480
that I was Lily Vale.

718
00:41:34,719 --> 00:41:35,679
I said I didn't know,

719
00:41:36,159 --> 00:41:37,159
and you didn't believe me, right?

720
00:41:40,480 --> 00:41:43,079
Didn't you say back in college

721
00:41:43,480 --> 00:41:44,239
you saw my article

722
00:41:44,239 --> 00:41:45,320
in a magazine

723
00:41:45,320 --> 00:41:46,400
and that inspired your dream?

724
00:41:48,400 --> 00:41:49,320
You're making yourself

725
00:41:49,320 --> 00:41:50,559
sound too heroic.

726
00:41:52,320 --> 00:41:53,880
You were copying back then, right?

727
00:42:01,119 --> 00:42:02,360
How can a copied story

728
00:42:02,920 --> 00:42:04,199
get so popular?

729
00:42:05,800 --> 00:42:06,719
I just wanted
the truth out.

730
00:42:09,119 --> 00:42:10,079
Didn't expect

731
00:42:10,679 --> 00:42:12,400
you'd crumble so easily.

732
00:42:17,440 --> 00:42:18,079
I only hired

733
00:42:18,079 --> 00:42:19,719
a few bots,

734
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:21,679
and you just…

735
00:42:25,480 --> 00:42:26,159
broke down?

736
00:42:33,159 --> 00:42:33,679
Come down!

737
00:42:33,760 --> 00:42:34,760
Chase me!

738
00:42:37,760 --> 00:42:39,239
Sorry, sis.

739
00:43:15,440 --> 00:43:16,400
Fun with the phone?

740
00:43:17,079 --> 00:43:19,280
Not bad. Haven't you tried it?

741
00:43:21,760 --> 00:43:22,599
Lend it to me for a sec.

742
00:43:31,519 --> 00:43:32,320
Caught red-handed.

743
00:43:33,519 --> 00:43:35,800
No excuses, hand it over.

744
00:43:45,360 --> 00:43:46,360
Director…

745
00:43:47,159 --> 00:43:47,760
Xu Huaishi!

746
00:43:49,480 --> 00:43:50,320
You're too much!

747
00:43:52,199 --> 00:43:53,639
You… you're really something!

748
00:43:53,639 --> 00:43:54,840
You actually handed
my phone to the teacher?

749
00:43:57,360 --> 00:43:59,639
So this phone's yours?

750
00:43:59,960 --> 00:44:00,679
Name's the same,
no switching,

751
00:44:02,039 --> 00:44:02,800
yours truly.

752
00:44:04,559 --> 00:44:05,360
Never thought

753
00:44:06,519 --> 00:44:07,039
you'd be into

754
00:44:07,039 --> 00:44:08,159
male celebs batting their lashes.

755
00:44:10,400 --> 00:44:11,039
No laughing!

756
00:44:18,440 --> 00:44:19,519
That's my freedom.

757
00:44:22,320 --> 00:44:23,119
Freedom, huh?

758
00:44:24,079 --> 00:44:24,760
There's words here too.

759
00:44:27,159 --> 00:44:28,440
'Shican,'

760
00:44:28,519 --> 00:44:29,360
'I love you forever.'

761
00:44:29,760 --> 00:44:30,719
Is this your freedom too?

762
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:35,679
This…

763
00:44:37,119 --> 00:44:38,159
I wrote it too.

764
00:44:38,880 --> 00:44:39,360
Well.

765
00:44:40,119 --> 00:44:40,960
So you wrote it.

766
00:44:41,760 --> 00:44:43,000
Then I wonder,

767
00:44:43,920 --> 00:44:45,360
why's your phone wallpaper

768
00:44:45,760 --> 00:44:46,239
her with

769
00:44:46,239 --> 00:44:47,519
a male star?

770
00:44:51,280 --> 00:44:52,000
What's that about?

771
00:44:53,280 --> 00:44:53,719
I…

772
00:44:55,840 --> 00:44:57,119
I'm shipping them.

773
00:44:57,280 --> 00:44:58,679
You can respond to anything, right?

774
00:44:59,079 --> 00:44:59,719
No laughing!

775
00:45:00,920 --> 00:45:02,239
You two, come to my office.

776
00:45:02,679 --> 00:45:03,559
No going home after school.

777
00:45:03,760 --> 00:45:04,360
Call your parents!

778
00:45:04,960 --> 00:45:06,679
[Log into your Huawei account first.]

779
00:45:06,960 --> 00:45:07,760
What the hell account!

780
00:45:16,559 --> 00:45:17,159
Thanks.

781
00:45:18,119 --> 00:45:18,920
For what?

782
00:45:19,719 --> 00:45:20,519
Didn't help you anyway.

783
00:45:21,519 --> 00:45:22,519
I'm not talking about that.

784
00:45:23,159 --> 00:45:23,800
Then what?

785
00:45:27,039 --> 00:45:28,079
You actually said

786
00:45:28,360 --> 00:45:29,840
Shican and I are a ship.
